      "Text": "Security update for xen",
      "Title": "Topic",
      "Type": "Summary"
    },
    {
      "Text": "This update for xen fixes the following issues:\n  \n- CVE-2024-31145: Fixed error handling in x86 IOMMU identity mapping (XSA-460, bsc#1228574)\n- CVE-2024-31146: Fixed PCI device pass-through with shared resources (XSA-461, bsc#1228575)\n\nOther fixes:\n- Update to Xen 4.18.3 security bug fix release (bsc#1027519)\n",
      "Title": "Details",
      "Type": "General"
